  "texts": [
    "To summarize, we found greater correct classification of internal content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.57 vs. R 2 = 0.00).",
    "We also found greater correct classification of external content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.37 vs. R 2 = 0.04).",
    "These results are summarized in Fig. 2 below.",
    "Our model correctly identified much of the internal content (Fig. 3a; r =.67, p < 0.001) and also correctly identified some of the external content (Fig.",
    "3b, r =.33, p < 0.001)."
  ]
